#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:12
msgid "Tools"
msgstr "ツール"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:12
msgid "Selection"
msgstr "選択"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:12
msgid "Similar Selection"
msgstr "近似選択"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:17
msgid "Similar Color Selection Tool"
msgstr "近似色選択ツール"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:19
msgid "|toolselectsimilar|"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:21
msgid ""
"This tool, represented by a dropper over an area with a dashed border, "
"allows you to make :ref:`selections_basics` by selecting a point of color. "
"It will select any areas of a similar color to the one you selected. You can "
"adjust the \"fuzziness\" of the tool in the tool options dock. A lower "
"number will select colors closer to the color that you chose in the first "
"place."
msgstr ""
"破線とスポイトで表されるこのツールは、色のあるところを選択すること"
"で :ref:`selections_basics` を作成できます。選択されたものに近い色があるエリ"
"アを選択します。ツールのオプションから\"あいまいさ\"を調節することができま"
"す。低い値にすれば最初に選んだ色により近い色を選択します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:25
msgid ""
"Most of the behavior of the Similar Color Selection Tool is common to all "
"other selection tools, please make sure to read :ref:`selections_basics` to "
"learn more about this tool."
msgstr ""
"近似色選択ツールのほとんどの機能は他の選択ツールと同じですので、詳しく"
"は :ref:`selections_basics` を見てください。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:29
msgid "Hotkeys and Sticky keys"
msgstr "ホットキーとスティッキーキー"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:31
msgid ""
":kbd:`Shift +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to 'add'. You can "
"release the :kbd:`Shift` key while dragging, but it will still be set to "
"'add'. Same for the others."
msgstr ""
":kbd:`Shift +` |mouseleft| で次される選択を'追加'します。ドラッグしなが"
"ら :kbd:`Shift` キーを離しても'追加'に設定されたままになります。他も同様で"
"す。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:32
msgid ":kbd:`Alt +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to 'subtract'."
msgstr ":kbd:`Alt +` |mouseleft| で次される選択を'除外'します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:33
msgid ":kbd:`Ctrl +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to 'replace'."
msgstr ":kbd:`Ctrl +` |mouseleft| で次される選択に'置換'します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:34
msgid ""
":kbd:`Shift + Alt +` |mouseleft| sets the subsequent selection to "
"'intersect'."
msgstr ""
":kbd:`Shift + Alt +` |mouseleft| で次される選択との'積集合'を取ります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:38
msgid ""
"Hovering your cursor over the dashed line of the selection, or marching ants "
"as it is commonly called, turns the cursor into the move tool icon, which "
"you |mouseleft| and drag to move the selection."
msgstr ""
"選択の破線にマウスホバーすることでカーソルが移動ツールアイコンに代わり、|"
"mouseleft| ドラッグで選択を移動することができます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:40
msgid ""
"|mouseright| will open up a selection quick menu with amongst others the "
"ability to edit the selection."
msgstr "|mouseright| で他の選択編集機能のある選択クイックメニューが開きます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:48
msgid ""
"You can switch the behavior of the :kbd:`Alt` key to use :kbd:`Ctrl` instead "
"by toggling the switch in Tool Settings in the :ref:`general_settings`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`general_settings` にあるツールの設定から :kbd:`Alt` キーと :kbd:`Ctrl` "
"キーの振る舞いを入れ替えることができます。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:52
msgid ""
"This tool is not bound to any Hotkey, if you want to define one, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> Configure Krita --> Keyboard Shortcuts` and "
"search for 'Similar Color Selection Tool', there you can select the shortcut "
"you want. Check :ref:`shortcut_settings` for more info."
msgstr ""
"このツールはどのホットキーにも割り当てられていませんので、定義するに"
"は :menuselection:`設定 --> Krita の設定を変更 --> キーボードショートカット` "
"に行き'近似色選択ツール'から設定したいショートカットを選ぶことができます。詳"
"しくは :ref:`shortcut_settings` を見てください。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:56
msgid "Tool Options"
msgstr "ツールのオプション"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:62
msgid "Action"
msgstr "動作"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:63
msgid "This option is explained in the :ref:`pixel_vector_selection` section."
msgstr ""
"このオプションについては :ref:`pixel_vector_selection` の項目で説明していま"
"す。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:65
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Selection"
msgid "Selection Extent"
msgstr "選択"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:65
msgid "Threshold"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:66
msgid ""
"This controls the range of the color hue used to create the selection. A "
"lower number will select colors closer to the color that you chose in the "
"first place. And a higher number will expand the hue range and select colors "
"even if they are not so similar to the original color."
msgstr ""
"選択作成に使われる色相の範囲を操作できます。低い値であれば最初に選択された色"
"により近い色を選択するようになります。高い値は色相の範囲を広げ、元の色にそん"
"なに近くなくても選択するようになります。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:70
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Anti-aliasing"
msgid "Anti-alias"
msgstr "アンチエイリアス"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:71
msgid ""
"This will smooth the jagged edges present in the region. It differs from "
"feathering in that this will smooth in the direction of the edge instead of "
"all directions, and only if the edge is jagged (high contrast)."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:73
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Selection"
msgid "Grow Selection"
msgstr "選択"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:74
msgid ""
"This value extends (positive values) or contracts (negative values) the "
"region."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:75
msgid "Adjustments"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:75
msgid "Feathering Radius"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:76
msgid "This value will add a soft border to the region."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:80
msgid ""
"Select which layers to use as a reference for the contiguous select tool. "
"The options are:"
msgstr ""
"近似色選択ツールでどのレイヤーを判定に使用するかを選択します。オプションは:"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:82
msgid "Current Layer"
msgstr "現在のレイヤー"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:83
msgid "Only use the currently selected layer."
msgstr "現在選択されているレイヤーのみを使用します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:84
msgid "All layers"
msgstr "すべてのレイヤー"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:85
msgid "Use all visible layers."
msgstr "すべての表示レイヤーを使用します。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:87
msgid ""
"Use only the layers specified with a certain color label. This is useful for "
"complex images, where you might have multiple lineart layers. Label them "
"with the appropriate color label and use these labels to mark which layers "
"to use as a reference."
msgstr ""
"特定の色ラベルが付いたレイヤーのみを使用します。複数の線画レイヤーがあるよう"
"な、複雑な画像に便利です。適当な色ラベルを付け判定に使用するレイヤーとして印"
"をつけるのに使います。"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:90
msgid "Select the color labels of the layers that should be used as reference."
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:92
msgid "Reference"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:92
msgid "Color Labeled Layers"
msgstr "色ラベル付きレイヤー"

#. +> trunk5
#: ../../reference_manual/tools/similar_select.rst:92
msgid "Labels Used"
msgstr "使用されたラベル"

